> Political Justices mull appeal of Chicago suburb's assault weapons ban This Oct. 13, 2015, photo shows the Supreme Court in Washington. The Supreme Court has so far resisted elaborating on two landmark decisions that established a nationwide right to defend one's home with a gun. That could change with a new appeal filed by gun owners that challenges a Chicago suburb's assault weapons ban.(AP Photo/Jacquelyn Martin) 
